[Center][B]Fatal Barrage[/B] [b][Fatal Barrage progress][/b] [B]20% Done so far[/B]
[B]Starting Date:[/B] 10/28/09 [B]Estimated Finish Date:[/B]Some time in December, of 2009 or January of 2010.
[B]What exactly is Fatal Barrage?[/B] Fatal Barrage is a 508 loading 525 cache source server. We focus on letting you, the players, have a fun and enjoyable time. Its not to easy to make money, but at the same time it is not to hard. As for training, it currently is 600xp per hit. All this combined makes a great economy. [URL=http://"Fatalbarrage.forumotion.com"]Click me for forums of Fatal Barrage[/URL]
This source is being programmed by [img]http://i39.tinypic.com/m83cw8.png[/img]Superwiz789

[center][b]What does Fatal Barrage have to offer you?[/center][/b] • Npccombat (Started, have some specials.
